---
title: Zucchini Chicken Gratin with Roasted Potatoes and Green Salad
description: Life’s most precious commodity is time and tonight we want to make sure you’ve got more of it to do stuff that counts. Get your kids to help you grate the zucchini for this yummy recipe to cut down on prep time (and increase some family bonding time!)
